text: Tutku Burcu Yüzgenç (born 15 January 1999) is a Turkish female volleyball player. She was part of the Turkish women's volleyball national team. She participated in the 2015 Girls' Youth European Volleyball Championship, 2015 FIVB Volleyball Girls' U18 World Championship, 2015 European Youth Summer Olympic Festival, 2016 FIVB World Grand Prix, and 2017 FIVB Volleyball Women's U20 World Championship. == References == Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Turkish volleyball players
